BUT tracking these symptoms can help us understand our bodies and cycle patterns so much better! 📅✨ 
Flo @flotracker is a premium period tracker app that offers valuable insights into female health alongside educational content from medical experts. 🩺💡 
It also connects you to a safe community of women👩‍👩‍👧‍👧 

For extra security, Flo has an anonymous mode! 🔒 
Luckily, the app is FREE for all Android users in India for one year! So go ahead and download it now! 📲❤️ https://floapp.onelink.me/eM4C/simmygoraya
